<l>paṟṟi viṭāa viṭumpaikaḷ paṟṟiṉaip</l>
<l>paṟṟi viṭāa tavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sorrows will never let go their hold of those who give not up their hold of desire.</l>
